txt.en: <rgb=#FF0000>Defeat Ugturu before he tires of fighting and leaves</rgb>
<rgb=#FF0000>You have left Ugturu unchallenged for too long.</rgb>
An enraged half-troll has come into the area. Defeat him before he does great damage!
Enough of this. Back to the ships!

The Half-troll brute, Ugturu, has come into the area. If left unchecked he will wreak colossal havoc. Dispense with him as quickly as possible.

This quest starts with <rgb=#FFFF00>empty</rgb> Merit Rating.

<rgb=#00FF00>Merit Gain:</rgb>
* Defeat Ugturu
* Defeat Ugturu quickly
<rgb=#FF0000>Defeat Ugturu before he tires of fighting and leaves</rgb>
Defeat Ugturu the Half-Troll quickly, before he does colossal damage.
